[Isela's Weaponry]
[Isela's General Store]
description: Enclosed by warped driftwood walls, the shop features a carved ebonwood dinghy in the center of its sand floor.  A woven black fishing net hangs under the driftwood ceiling.  Right near the front is a wide knotted oak counter and a splintered cargo crate.
